<font face="Serif" size="18">よし</font>

70
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,560
<font face="Serif" size="18">こちらへどうぞ</font>

71
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:06,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">暑くてたまらない</font>

72
